#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:855
msgid ""
"<b>Enable dark theme:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the system theme is asked to use a darker styling for the "
"application <i>(i.e. dark UI elements on bright text)</i>.\n"
"\n"
"Note that not all system themes provide such a darker variant, therefore "
"enabling this setting might not have an effect."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ku kunna jigon duhu:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, ana buƙatar jigon tsarin don amfani da salo mai duhu don aikace-aikacen <i>(watau abubuwan UI masu duhu akan rubutu mai haske)</i>.\n"
"\n"
"Lura cewa ba duk jigogin tsarin ke ba da irin wannan bambance-bambancen duhu ba, don haka kunna wannan saitin bazai yi tasiri ba."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:873
msgid ""
"<b>Enable client-side decorations:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search entry and main menu are displayed in the window title "
"bar.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the main menu is displayed as a menu bar with the search entry "
"below it.\n"
"This resembles a more traditional UI layout and takes a little bit more "
"space."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ku kunna kayan ado na gefen abokin ciniki:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, ana nuna shigarwar bincike da babban menu a mashigin taken taga.\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kashe, ana nuna babban menu azaman mashaya menu tare da shigarwar binciken ƙasa.\n"
"Wannan yayi kama da shimfidar UI na gargajiya kuma yana ɗaukar ɗan sarari kaɗan."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:893
msgid ""
"<b>Use binary units instead of decimal units:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This settings controls how file sizes are displayed.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Binary units:</b> This refers to binary IEC prefixes <i>(e.g. 1 KiB = "
"1024 bytes)</i>\n"
"\t• <b>Decimal  units:</b> This refers to decimal SI prefixes <i>(e.g. 1 kB "
"= 1000 bytes)</i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Ayi amfani da raka'o'in binary maimakon raka'a goma:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan saitin yana sarrafa yadda ake nuna girman fayil.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Raka'a binary:</b> Wannan yana nufin binaryar IEC prefixes <i>(misali 1 KiB = 1024 bytes)</i>\n"
"\t• <b>Raka'a Decimal:</b> Wannan yana nufin prefixes SI decimal <i>(misali 1 kB = 1000 bytes)</i>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:913
msgid ""
"<b>Remember window size:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the window size from the previous session will be restored when "
"you open an FSearch window.\n"
"\n"
"Note that some window managers ignore this request and force the window to "
"have a different size."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tuna girman taga:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, za a dawo da girman taga daga zaman da ya gabata lokacin da ka buɗe taga FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"Lura cewa wasu manajan taga sunyi watsi da wannan buƙatar kuma suna tilasta taga ta sami girman daban."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:932
msgid ""
"<b>Behaviour after successfully opening a file:</b>\n"
"\n"
"When a file/folder was successfully opened one of the following actions can "
"be performed:\n"
"\t• <b>Nothing:</b> Nothing happens.\n"
"                        • <b>Minimize:</b> The currently selected FSearch "
"window becomes minimized.\n"
"\t• <b>Close:</b> Quit FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"You can configure if those actions should be triggered when the file was "
"opened with\n"
"\t• <b>keyboard shortcuts or menu entries</b> and/or\n"
"\t• <b>mouse click</b>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Halayyar bayan nasarar buɗe fayil:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Lokacin da aka yi nasarar buɗe fayil/fayil ɗin cikin nasara ana iya aiwatar da ɗayan ayyuka masu zuwa:\n"
"\t• <b>Babu:</b> Babu wani abu da zai faru.\n"
"                        • <b>Rage:</b> Tagan FSearch da aka zaɓa a halin yanzu yana zama raguwa.\n"
"\t• <b>Rufe:</b> Bar FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"Kuna iya saita idan waɗannan ayyukan ya kamata a jawo lokacin da aka buɗe fayil ɗin tare da\n"
"\t• <b>Gajerun hanyoyin allo ko shigarwar menu</b> da/ko\n"
"\t• <b>latsa linzamin kwamfuta</b>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:956
msgid ""
"<b>Show highlighted search terms:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search terms will be highlighted in the results view. For "
"example when you search for \"foo\" all appearances of <i>foo</i> in file/"
"folder names will be highlighted with bold characters:\n"
"\n"
"\t<b>foo</b>bar.txt\n"
"\tfile.<b>foo</b>\n"
"\n"
"This also works for regular expressions and wildcard expressions starting or "
"ending with an asterisk. "
msgstr ""
"<b>Nuna fitattun sharuddan nema:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, za a haskaka sharuɗɗan bincike a cikin sakamakon binciken. Misali idan ka nemo \\\"foo\\\" duk bayyanar <i>foo</i> a cikin fayil/fayil sunaye za a haskaka su da haruffa masu ƙarfin gaske:\n"
"\n"
"\t<b>foo</b>bar.txt\n"
"\tfayil.<b>foo</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan kuma yana aiki don maganganu na yau da kullun da kalamai masu ban sha'awa waɗanda farawa ko ƙarewa tare da alamar alama."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:978
msgid ""
"<b>Show tooltips:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the results view will show the full path of the focused file/"
"folder in a small tooltip window."
msgstr ""
"<b>Nuna kayan aiki:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, kallon sakamakon zai nuna cikakken hanyar fayil/fayil da aka mayar da hankali a cikin ƙaramin taga kayan aiki."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:995
msgid ""
"<b>Show icons in name column:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, file/folder icons will be shown in the name column."
msgstr ""
"<b>Nuna gumaka a ginshiƙin suna:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, za a nuna gumakan fayil/fayil a cikin ginshiƙin suna."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1012
msgid ""
"<b>Remember column configuration:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the column configuration of the results view from the previous "
"session will be restored when you open an FSearch window. This includes the "
"size and visibility of all columns."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tuna daidaitawar shafi:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, za a dawo da tsarin ginshiƙi na ra'ayin sakamakon daga zaman da ya gabata lokacin da ka buɗe taga FSearch. Wannan ya haɗa da girma da ganuwa na duk ginshiƙai."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1029
msgid ""
"<b>Remember sort order:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the sort order of the results view from the previous session "
"will be restored when you open an FSearch window."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ka tuna da tsari:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, za a dawo da nau'in tsari na kallon sakamakon da aka samu daga zaman da ya gabata lokacin da ka buɗe taga FSearch."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1046
msgid ""
"<b>Open path with double click in path column:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, double clicking in the path column will open the selected path."
msgstr ""
"<b>Bude hanya tare da danna sau biyu a ginshiƙin hanya:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, danna sau biyu a cikin ginshiƙin hanya zai buɗe hanyar da aka zaɓa."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1063
msgid ""
"<b>Single click to open:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, a single click will open the selected file/folder. If you only "
"want to select a file/folder while this setting is active, you need to hold "
"<i>Ctrl</i> at the same time while clicking the file/folder."
msgstr ""
"<b>Latsa guda don buɗewa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, dannawa ɗaya zai buɗe fayil/fayil ɗin da aka zaɓa. Idan kawai kuna son zaɓar fayil / babban fayil yayin wannan saitin yana aiki, kuna buƙatar riƙe <i>Ctrl</i> a lokaci guda yayin danna fayil / babban fayil."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1080
msgid ""
"<b>Show database indexing status:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the path that is currently being indexed is displayed in the "
"statusbar."
msgstr ""
"<b>Nuna matsayin bayanan bayanai:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, hanyar da a halin yanzu ake ƙididdigewa tana nunawa a ma'aunin matsayi."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1097
msgid ""
"<b>Show warning dialogs:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, a warning dialog is displayed when a file or folder failed to "
"open."
msgstr ""
"<b>Nuna maganganun faɗakarwa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, ana nuna maganganun faɗakarwa lokacin da fayil ko babban fayil ya kasa buɗewa."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1114
msgid ""
"<b>Search in path when query contains path separators:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, search terms containing path separators (i.e. \"/\") will be "
"automatically matched against the full path of a file or folder."
msgstr ""
"<b>Bincika a hanya lokacin da tambaya ta ƙunshi masu raba hanya:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, kalmomin bincike masu ɗauke da masu raba hanya (watau \\\"/\\\") za a daidaita su ta atomatik da cikakken hanyar fayil ko babban fayil."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1131
msgid ""
"<b>Match case when query contains at least one upper case character:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, search terms containing at least one upper case character will "
"trigger a case-sensitive search. This means a search term like <i>Foo</i> "
"will match <i>FooBar.txt</i> but not <i>foobar.txt</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Harkokin daidaitawa lokacin da tambaya ta ƙunshi aƙalla harafi guda ɗaya:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, sharuɗɗan bincike mai ƙunshe da aƙalla babban harafi ɗaya zai haifar da bincike mai ma'ana. Wannan yana nufin kalmar nema kamar <i>Foo</i> zata dace da <i>FooBar.txt</i> amma ba <i>foobar.txt</i> ba."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1148
msgid ""
"<b>Hide results when search is empty:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, no search results are displayed when the search entry is empty.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, all files and folders will be displayed when the search entry "
"is empty."
msgstr ""
"<b>Boye sakamakon idan babu komai:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, ba za a nuna sakamakon bincike ba lokacin da shigarwar binciken ba ta da komai.\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kashe, duk fayiloli da manyan fayiloli za a nuna su lokacin da shigarwar binciken ya zama fanko."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1167
msgid ""
"<b>Search as you type:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search is automatically updated with every keystroke.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the search is only updated when you hit <i>Enter</i> or press "
"the search button. "
msgstr ""
"<b>Bincika yayin da kuke bugawa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, ana sabunta binciken ta atomatik tare da kowane maɓalli.\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kashe, ana sabunta binciken ne kawai lokacin da ka buga <i>Enter</i> ko danna maɓallin nema."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1186
msgid ""
"<b>Update database on start:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the database will be updated automatically in the background "
"when you start FSearch."
msgstr ""
"<b>Sabunta bayanai tun farko:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, za a sabunta bayanan bayanan ta atomatik a bango lokacin da kuka fara FSearch."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1203
msgid ""
"<b>Included folders:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This list contains all folders you want to include in the database.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> If enabled, the path will included in the database to be "
"searched in.\n"
"\t• <b>Path:</b> The full path to be included.\n"
"\t• <b>One Filesystem:</b> If enabled, FSearch won't cross filesystem "
"boundaries for this folder"
msgstr ""
"<b>Hade manyan manyan fayiloli:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan jeri ya ƙunshi duk manyan fayiloli da kuke son haɗawa a cikin bayanan.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> Idan an kunna hanyar, za a haɗa hanyar a cikin bayanan da za a bincika a ciki.\n"
"\t• <b>Hanya:</b> Cikakken hanyar da za a haɗa.\n"
"\t• <b>Tsarin Fayil guda ɗaya:</b> Idan an kunna, FSearch ba zai ketare iyakokin tsarin fayil na wannan babban fayil ɗin ba."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1224
msgid ""
"<b>Add folder to database:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can select a folder you want to include "
"in the database for searching."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ƙara babban fayil zuwa bayanan bayanai:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan maballin yana buɗe zance inda zaku iya zaɓar babban fayil ɗin da kuke son sakawa a cikin ma'ajin bayanai don bincike."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1241
msgid ""
"<b>Add a specific path:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Type the full path of a folder here and click the button next to it to "
"include that folder in the database. This is useful for adding a path "
"directly without browsing for it."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ƙara takamaiman hanya:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Buga cikakken hanyar babban fayil anan kuma danna maballin kusa da shi don haɗa wannan babban fayil ɗin a cikin bayanan. Wannan yana da amfani don ƙara hanya kai tsaye ba tare da bincika ta ba."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1258
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected row:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This removes the selected folder from the list of included folders."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cire zaɓaɓɓen jere:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan yana cire babban fayil ɗin da aka zaɓa daga jerin manyan fayilolin da aka haɗa."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1275
msgid ""
"<b>Attempt to monitor:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch watches this folder for changes and keeps the database "
"up to date automatically, so you don't have to rescan manually.\n"
"\n"
"Monitoring isn't supported on every file system and uses a small amount of "
"system resources per watched folder. For large directory trees with many "
"files the system may run out of resources to watch them all."
msgstr ""
"<b>Yi ƙoƙarin saka idanu:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, FSearch yana kallon wannan babban fayil don canje-canje kuma yana adana bayanan da aka sabunta ta atomatik, don haka ba lallai ne ku sake bincika da hannu ba.\n"
"\n"
"Ba a tallafawa sa ido akan kowane tsarin fayil kuma yana amfani da ƙaramin adadin albarkatun tsarin kowace babban fayil da ake kallo. Don manyan bishiyoyin adireshi masu fayiloli da yawa tsarin na iya ƙarewa da albarkatun don kallon su duka."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1294
msgid ""
"<b>Scan after launch:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, this folder is rescanned every time FSearch starts, so the "
"database reflects any changes made while FSearch wasn't running."
msgstr ""
"<b>Duba bayan ƙaddamarwa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, wannan babban fayil ana sake dubawa duk lokacin da FSearch ya fara, don haka ma'aunin bayanai yana nuna duk wani canje-canje da aka yi yayin FSearch baya aiki."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1311
msgid ""
"<b>Stay on one file system:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch won't cross file system boundaries while scanning this "
"folder. Mounted file systems below it (e.g. external drives or network "
"shares) are skipped."
msgstr ""
"<b>Zama akan tsarin fayil ɗaya:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, FSearch ba zai ketare iyakokin tsarin fayil ba yayin bincika wannan babban fayil ɗin. An tsallake tsarin fayilolin da aka ɗora a ƙarƙashinsa (misali fayafai na waje ko hannun jari na cibiyar sadarwa)."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1328
msgid ""
"<b>Rescan every:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, this folder is rescanned automatically at the given interval. "
"Use the hours and minutes fields to set how often the rescan happens.\n"
"\n"
"This is useful for folders on file systems that can't be monitored for "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"<b>Sake dubawa kowane:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna wannan babban fayil ɗin ana sake duba ta ta atomatik a lokacin da aka bayar. Yi amfani da sa'o'i da filayen mintuna don saita sau nawa sake dubawa ya faru.\n"
"\n"
"Wannan yana da amfani ga manyan fayiloli akan tsarin fayil waɗanda ba za a iya sa ido ba don canje-canje."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1347
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude rules:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This list contains rules for the files and folders you want to exclude from "
"the database.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> If enabled, the rule is applied and matching items are "
"excluded.\n"
"\t• <b>Pattern:</b> The text matched against each item, interpreted "
"according to the Type.\n"
"\t• <b>Type:</b> How the pattern is interpreted — <i>Literal</i> (exact "
"text), <i>Wildcard</i> (using * and ?) or <i>Regex</i> (a regular "
"expression).\n"
"\t• <b>Match:</b> Whether the pattern is matched against the item's <i>Full "
"Path</i> or only its <i>Basename</i> (the name without the path).\n"
"\t• <b>Applies To:</b> Whether the rule affects <i>Files</i>, <i>Folders</i> "
"or both."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ba da dokoki:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan jeri ya ƙunshi dokoki don fayiloli da manyan fayilolin da kuke son cirewa daga ma'ajin bayanai.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> Idan an kunna, ana amfani da ƙa'idar kuma an cire abubuwan da suka dace.\n"
"\t• <b>Tsarin:</b> Rubutun ya yi daidai da kowane abu, an fassara shi gwargwadon Nau'in.\n"
"\t• <b>Nau'i:</b> Yadda ake fassara tsarin - <i>Literal</i> (ainihin rubutu), <i>Wildcard</i> (amfani da * da ?) ko <i>Regex</i> (kalmomi na yau da kullun).\n"
"\t• <b>Match:</b> Ko tsarin ya yi daidai da abin <i>Cikakken Hanya</i> ko kuma kawai <i>Basename</i> (sunan ba tare da hanya ba).\n"
"\t• <b>Ya shafi:</b> Ko ka'idar ta shafi <i>Fayloli</i>, <i>Fayloli</i> ko duka biyun."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1370
msgid ""
"<b>Add exclude rule:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This adds a new, empty rule to the list. Edit its Pattern, Type, Match and "
"Applies To columns to control what gets excluded from the database."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ƙara ƙa'idar cirewa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan yana ƙara sabuwar doka mara komai a lissafin. Shirya Tsarin sa, Nau'insa, Daidaita da Aiwatar da su zuwa ginshiƙai don sarrafa abin da aka cire daga bayanan."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1387
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected row:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This removes the selected rule from the list of exclude rules."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cire zaɓaɓɓen jere:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan yana cire ƙa'idar da aka zaɓa daga jerin ƙa'idodin keɓe."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1404
msgid ""
"<b>Restore default exclude rules:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button restores the default set of exclude rules.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ All rules which were created or edited by the user will be lost! ⚠"
msgstr ""
"<b>Mayar da tsoffin ƙa'idodi:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan maballin yana dawo da tsoffin saitin ƙa'idodin ware.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ Duk ƙa'idodin da mai amfani ya ƙirƙira ko ya gyara za su ɓace! ⚠"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1423
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude files and folders from database:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This is a semi-colon separated list of files (or folders) you want to "
"exclude from the database. For example <i>.git;.cache;*.swp</i> will exclude "
"all files or folders which are called either <i>.git</i> or <i>.cache</i> or "
"end with <i>.swp</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cire fayiloli da manyan fayiloli daga bayanan bayanai:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan jerin manyan fayiloli ne (ko manyan fayiloli) da kuke son cirewa daga bayanan bayanai. Misali <i>.git;.cache;*.swp</i> zai ware duk fayiloli ko manyan fayiloli da ake kira <i>.git</i> ko <i>.cache</i> ko kuma su ƙare da <i>.swp</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1440
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude hidden files and folders:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, hidden files and folders will be excluded from the database "
"<i>(i.e. all files or folders which start with a dot character)</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Baya ɓoye fayiloli da manyan fayiloli:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, za a cire ɓoye fayiloli da manyan fayiloli daga rumbun adana bayanai <i>(watau duk fayiloli ko manyan fayiloli waɗanda suka fara da alamar digo)</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1457
msgid "Focus a setting to get a detailed description of what it does."
msgstr "Mayar da hankali wuri don samun cikakken bayanin abin da yake yi."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1470
msgid ""
"<b>Periodically update database at a specific time interval:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled and as long as FSearch is running, the database will be updated "
"periodically with the given time interval.\n"
"\n"
"If you want to update the database in the background, even when FSearch is "
"not running, you should use tools like cron or systemd timers to "
"periodically trigger the update with:\n"
"\n"
"<i><tt>fsearch --update-database</tt></i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Lokaci sabunta bayanan bayanai a wani tazara na musamman:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna kuma muddin FSearch yana gudana, za a sabunta bayanan lokaci-lokaci tare da tazarar lokacin da aka ba.\n"
"\n"
"Idan kuna son sabunta bayanan bayanan a bango, koda lokacin FSearch baya gudana, yakamata kuyi amfani da kayan aikin kamar cron ko masu ƙidayar lokaci don kunna sabuntawa lokaci-lokaci tare da:\n"
"\n"
"<i><tt>fsearch --update-database</tt></i>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1491
msgid ""
"<b>Launch desktop files:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, activating a <i>.desktop</i> file will launch the application "
"defined within that file. This way FSearch can act like an application "
"launcher. Otherwise the <i>.desktop</i> file will be opened with the default "
"handler for this type of files, which is usually a text editor."
msgstr ""
"<b>Kaddamar da fayilolin tebur:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, kunna fayil na <i>.desktop</i> zai ƙaddamar da aikace-aikacen da aka ayyana cikin wannan fayil ɗin. Ta wannan hanyar FSearch na iya aiki kamar mai ƙaddamar da aikace-aikacen. In ba haka ba za a buɗe fayil ɗin <i>.desktop</i> tare da tsoho mai kula da irin wannan nau'in fayiloli, wanda galibi editan rubutu ne."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1508
msgid ""
"<b>Filters:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This is a list of all available filters. A filter is a predefined search.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Name:</b> A unique and descriptive identifier for the filter\n"
"\t• <b>Macro:</b> By typing the macro text followed by a ':' you can enable "
"the filter on demand\n"
"\t• <b>Query:</b> The search term by which the database should be filtered"
msgstr ""
"<b>Tace:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan jerin duk abubuwan tacewa. Tace bincike ne da aka riga aka kayyade.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Sunan:</b> Mahimmanci na musamman da siffantawa don tacewa\n"
"\t• <b>Macro:</b> Ta hanyar buga macro rubutu da ':' za ku iya kunna tacewa akan buƙata.\n"
"\t• <b>Tambaya:</b> Kalmomin bincike da ya kamata a tace bayanan"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1529
msgid ""
"<b>Add a new filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can edit a new filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ƙara sabon tacewa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan maɓallin yana buɗe maganganu inda za ku iya gyara sabon tacewa."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1546
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button removes the currently selected filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cire zaɓaɓɓen tacewa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan maɓallin yana cire tacewa a halin yanzu da aka zaɓa."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1563
msgid ""
"<b>Edit selected filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can edit the selected filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>A gyara zaɓaɓɓen tacewa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan maɓallin yana buɗe maganganu inda za ku iya gyara zaɓaɓɓen tacewa."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1580
msgid ""
"<b>Restore default filters:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button restores the default filter configuration.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ All filters which were created or edited by the user will be lost! ⚠"
msgstr ""
"<b>Mayar da tsoffin tacewa:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Wannan maballin yana dawo da saitunan tace tsoho.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ Duk matattarar da mai amfani ya ƙirƙira ko gyara za su ɓace! ⚠"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1599
msgid ""
"<b>Exit on Escape:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch exits when the Escape key is pressed instead of the "
"window being minimized."
msgstr ""
"<b>Fita akan Gudu:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Idan an kunna, FSearch yana fita lokacin da aka danna maɓallin Tserewa maimakon rage girman taga."

